<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <title>Страница не найдена</title>
    <style>
        .not-found-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .not-found-container h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ef4444;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .not-found-container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .not-found-container a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .not-found-container a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .search-form {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .search-form input {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .search-form button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .search-form button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .not-found-container {
                margin: 2rem;
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .search-form {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .search-form input,
            .search-form button {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="not-found-container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Страница не найдена</p>
        <p>К сожалению, запрашиваемая страница не существует.</p>
        <p>Попробуйте вернуться на <a href="/">главную страницу</a>.</p>

    </div>

    <form id="search-form" action="/search" method="get" style="display: none;"></form>
</body>
</html>